item.title: Asparagus fern houseplant
item.dc:creator: vonhan
item.description: Our houseplant friends never forget their roots, and they’ll always be the most content when their surroundings mimic their natural environment. This spiky show off is native to South Africa and loves a bit of shade and a bit of sun, so bright indirect light is the perfect combo. Buy this product on graceandthorn.com
